@HomeLink_HostAddress = http://localhost:5119

### Health check
GET {{HomeLink_HostAddress}}/health

###

### ── Display ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### Render full display — returns raw 1bpp binary (application/octet-stream)
GET {{HomeLink_HostAddress}}/api/display/render
Accept: application/octet-stream

###

### Render full display — with dithering disabled and device battery hint
GET {{HomeLink_HostAddress}}/api/display/render?dither=false&deviceBattery=42
Accept: application/octet-stream

###

### Render display as PNG image (human-readable preview)
GET {{HomeLink_HostAddress}}/api/display/image
Accept: image/png

###

### Render display as PNG — dithering off, with battery indicator
GET {{HomeLink_HostAddress}}/api/display/image?dither=false&deviceBattery=6
Accept: image/png

###

### Render Spotify section only — returns JSON bitmap (useful for testing Spotify section)
GET {{HomeLink_HostAddress}}/api/display/render-spotify-only
Accept: application/json

###

### Render location section only — uses cached OwnTracks location, returns JSON bitmap
### (send a POST /api/location/owntracks first if no location is cached)
GET {{HomeLink_HostAddress}}/api/display/render-location-only
Accept: application/json

###

### ── Location ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### Receive OwnTracks location update (POST — used by OwnTracks app)
POST {{HomeLink_HostAddress}}/api/location/owntracks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "_type": "location",
  "lat": 48.2082,
  "lon": 16.3738,
  "acc": 10,
  "alt": 180,
  "batt": 85,
  "bs": 1,
  "vel": 0,
  "tst": 1708560000,
  "tid": "AB"
}

###

### ── Telemetry ────────────────────────────────────────────

### Telemetry summary (default window)
GET {{HomeLink_HostAddress}}/api/telemetry/summary
Accept: application/json

###

### Telemetry summary — last hour, 1-minute resolution, max 60 data points
GET {{HomeLink_HostAddress}}/api/telemetry/summary?window=1h&resolution=1m&maxPoints=60
Accept: application/json

###

### Telemetry dashboard (HTML page)
GET {{HomeLink_HostAddress}}/telemetry/dashboard
Accept: text/html

